steps.html_instructions: Head east on Cadillac Square toward Bates St
Take the 2nd right onto Randolph Street

Turn right onto M-10 N/Jefferson Ave
Continue to follow M-10 N
Take exit 2A for I-75 toward Toledo/Flint
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-75 S/Toledo

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-75 S/Toledo and merge onto I-75 S
Entering Ohio
Take exit 208 on the left for I-280 S toward Turnpike/Cleveland
Keep right to continue toward I-280 S
Continue onto I-280 S
Continue straight onto OH-420 S
Keep left at the fork to continue on Exit 1B, follow signs for U.S. 20 E/U.S.23 S/Fremont
Keep left to continue toward US-20 E/US-23 S
Continue onto US-20 E/US-23 S
Turn right onto US-23 S
Turn left onto W South St
W South St turns right and becomes Midblock Upas
Midblock Upas turns left and becomes W Lytle St

Slight right onto US-23 S/Fostoria-Carey Rd
Continue to follow US-23 S
Turn right onto the US-23 S ramp to Columbus
Continue onto US-23 S
Keep left to stay on US-23 S, follow signs for Columbus
Continue straight onto US-23 S/Columbus Pike
Turn right onto OH-315 S
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit and stay on OH-315 S
Take the Interstate 71 S exit on the left toward Cincinnati
Merge onto I-71 S
Take exit 101 for I-270 toward Wheeling/Dayton
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-270/Wheeling and merge onto I-270 E
Take exit 52 to merge onto US-23 S toward Circleville

Continue onto US-35 E/US-50 E (signs for Jackson/Athens)
Continue to follow US-35 E
Entering West Virginia
Continue onto US-35
Take the Interstate 64 E ramp to St. Albans/Charleston
Merge onto I-64 E
Take exit 58C for US-60/Lee St

Turn right onto US-60 E/Lee St W
Continue to follow US-60 E
Turn right onto Dickinson St
